| id     | int(10) unsigned | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| name   | varchar(150)     | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| salary | double           | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| start  | date             | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
+--------+------------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
